1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e5 3. dxe5 Ng4 4. Bf4 Nc6 5. Nf3 Bb4+ 6. Nbd2 Qe7 7. e3 Ngxe5 8. Nxe5 Nxe5 9. a3 Bxd2+ 10. Qxd2 O-O 11. c5 d6 12. cxd6 cxd6 13. Be2 Be6 { White to play - training position (exploiting the weak pawn)
