{ Which file to control? } { [%csl Gc8,Gf8,Ge5][%cal Ga8c8,Ga8f8,Gf7f6,Gf6e5,Gf4e5] }
1... Ba6 2. Rf2 { Trade of rooks won't help you much
If you can't take over the file, no way in - trade of rooks (if you have other advantages in the position) } { [%cal Ga8f8,Gf2f8,Gg8f8] } 2... Rc8 { Black doesn't have an entry point down the c-file } { [%csl Gc1,Gc3][%cal Gc8c1,Gf2c2] } (2... Rf8 3. Rxf8+ Kxf8 { [%csl Ge4,Ge7,Ga6][%cal Gf8f7,Gf7g6,Gg6f5,Gf5e4,Gg7g5,Ga6c4,Gb2b3,Ga2a3] }) *


