, worauf sich das Spiel verschärft, besser war. (Botvinnik 1984) }) 21. Rad1 Ref8 22. f3 { A loosening of the kig position which cannot be avoided here,
beacuse it was impossible to protect the f-pawn with the rook and thus condemn
