Kozul's games as Black } { [%csl Gf8,Gd7][%cal Gf4f5,Ga8c8,Gh8g8] } (11... Qxf6 12. e5 dxe5 13. Ndxb5!) 12. f5 { The idea of weakening the light squares of the opponent's
