1. Advance the rook's pawn
2. Exchange their pieces to stop their attack
3. Set up a strong sacrifice to attack their king/take the initiative } 15. Nd4 Bg5 16. Rf3 a5 17. bxa5 Qxa5 18. Rg3 h6 19. Kh1 Nf6 20. Nb3 Qb6 21. N1d2 Bxe3 22. Qd3 Ra4 23. h3 Bf4 24. Rf3 Bc7 25. Nd4 Qd6 26. Nf1 Bb6 27. Qb5 Raa8 28. Nf5 Qe6 29. N1g3 Ra5 30. Qb4 Bc7 31. Raf1 Qe5 32. Re3 Ne4 33. Rfe1 Rxa2 34. Qb5 Nxg3+ 35. Nxg3 Qxe3 36. Rxe3 { 0-1 White resigns. } 0-1


