{ Enjoy the tournament - Bernard Laugery 'In chess, there are winners and there are learners'. Everyone in chess is a learner :)

Chess is a vast ocean - for beginners it's like swimming a few laps.

Chess is a sea where a gnat may drink and an elephant may bathe.

Isle of Man 2017 - won by Carlsen. First tournament win in 14 months. (Carlsen-Giri)

Are my pieces safe? Are my opponent's pieces safe? }
